# Rust
/target/
# Build dirs of workspace-excluded helper crates (e.g. the offline tools/gen-fingerprints generator).
tools/*/target/
Cargo.lock
# …but commit the desktop binary's lock: it's a workspace-EXCLUDED app whose Tauri
# dependency graph floats into broken upstream releases (brotli 8.0.3, pcre2) on a
# fresh CI/release resolve. A committed lock makes the desktop build reproducible.
!apps/indexa-desktop/Cargo.lock

# IDE
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
.DS_Store

# Indexa runtime data (never commit the user's index)
.indexa/

# Build artifacts
*.pdb
dist/

# Local environment secrets (never commit API keys)
.env
.env.*
dart_defines.json
